    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNV2">
      <l>mutalkaru vaṇainta vuripporu ḷakamē</l></lg>
<p xml:lang="en"><hi rend="italic">akam</hi> is <hi rend="italic">mutal</hi> and <hi rend="italic">karu</hi> together with <hi rend="italic">uripporul</hi>.</p>
      </div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
<p xml:id="TNV2comm1">e – tu. collappaṭṭaṉavaṟṟuḷ akapporuḷ āmāṟu uṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p xml:id="TNV2comm2">(i – ḷ.) mutaluṅ karuvuñ cārnta uripporuḷ akapporuḷ ām eṉṟavāṟu.</p>  
<p xml:id="TNV2comm3">mutal eṉappaṭṭatu viṭamum kālamum eṉṟuṇarvatu. karu veṉappaṭṭa poruḷ ceykai yoḻittuk koḷka. 
atuvum uriyum paṇpeṉappaṭum; innāṉkiṉ kūṭṭamum tiṇai yeṉappaṭum eṉpatu. (2)</p>
</body></text><standOff corresp="#TNV2" type="wordsplit">
